Class ExifMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • tif.ExifMetadata
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MetadataStrategy<DirectoryIFD>, java.lang.Iterable<DirectoryIFD>, ExifStrategy

    public class ExifMetadata
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExifStrategy
    A concrete metadata strategy for handling EXIF metadata, which is typically found in TIFF and JPEG files. This class stores and provides access to various Image File Directories (IFDs), such as the primary IFD, and EXIF sub-IFD. *

    This class implements the ExifStrategy interface, defining the specific behaviours required for managing EXIF data, including checking for the presence of the EXIF sub-directory.
